description "Imperial Shocktrooper [Clonetrooper]

Strengths: Heavy Hitter with a Solid Offense
Weaknesses: Weaker Armour 

^2Weapons:
- SE-14c Blaster Pistol (2)
- DLT-19 Repeater (2)
- 2 Concussive Grenades
- 2 Sonic Detonators

^6Inventory:
- Portable Sentry Gun

^8Attributes:
- Armor Regen (1)
- Stamina (1)
- 1 Reinforcement
- Rally

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]
- Dodge (2) ^3[CS2]

Part of the Imperial Stormtrooper Corps, Imperial Shocktroopers act as a Security Police Force, working to bring down criminals and uphold Imperial Law."
